if [ ! -f "/data/warpgate.yaml" ]; then
  echo "Initializing Warpgate..."
  warpgate unattended-setup --data-path /data --http-port 8888 --ssh-port 2222 --mysql-port 33306 --postgres-port 55432
else
  echo "Warpgate already initialized, starting normally..."
  warpgate run
fi
